name: cfe-property-list-editor
displayName: A user friendly, translatable name of the component.
description: A translatable high-level description for the component.

propertyListName.description: Name of property list, which should be set to property name specified in PDJ.

propertiesString.description: JSON string that represents the object with name and value pair.

readonly.description: Indicates if this property list editor is read only, defaults to false.

deleteButtonTooltip.description: Tooltip for the trash can icon

getPropertyListChangeResults.description: Returns JS object for latest property list entries.

updatePropertyListSnapshot.description: Update snapshot of property list entries.
